UPDATE [dbo].[tblDynamicPage] SET RowUpdatedDateTime = GetDate(),  dynamicValue = '{"Form":"auto-finance","Title":"Simpler auto financing for all at DriveTime in %REGION%.","Paragraphs":[["Is your credit score keeping you from getting the car you deserve? For auto financing in %REGION%, DriveTime dealers are a great option for discerning buyers with no credit or low credit problems. Regardless of your financial past, %REGION% auto financing dealers are standing by to get you into the car, truck, or van that you need. When other dealers say “no,” we are here to say “yes.”","Having a low credit score can make it difficult to obtain auto financing in %REGION%, but now individuals of all financial histories have hope. At DriveTime dealerships, customers with low or no credit have access to several used vehicle options - including cars, trucks, and vans - to meet their unique needs. Despite financial troubles in the past, poor credit auto financing dealers are ready to help you drive home happy today.","Looking for poor credit auto financing in %REGION%? Look no further than DriveTime, where customers with all types of credit histories can get financed for used cars that other dealerships often will not finance for subprime credit score customers. Whether you are looking for a van, car, or truck, DriveTime has tons of vehicles to choose from with payment options you need to get behind the wheel and start driving today.","Securing auto financing in %REGION% may seem impossible for those who have faced financial difficulties or have not built strong credit histories. DriveTime dealers are the answer for many consumers. Regardless of past credit problems, DriveTime looks at credit worthiness differently to help individuals secure financing while driving home in the used vehicle.  Find out why we stand out among other %REGION% auto financing dealers."],["Unlike other used car dealerships offering poor credit auto financing in %REGION%, DriveTime is committed to providing a large selection of pre-owned vehicles, all inspected* and including a 30-day/1,500-mile limited warranty. When you arrive at our auto financing dealership, one of our staff members will work with you to find the right car for you. Our competitors may stock their lots with overpriced, worn-out vehicles, but DriveTime %REGION% auto financing dealers strive to find the best fit of financing and vehicle for each and every customer.","Many poor credit auto financing dealers get away with stocking undesirable used vehicles, but not at DriveTime. Each automobile receives a pre-purchase inspection* and a 30-day/1,500-mile limited warranty, giving customers confidence in their investment. Talk with our skilled sales staff to find the perfect vehicle, and you too can benefit from the commitment to customer service DriveTime offers its clients.","Unfortunately, the majority of %REGION% auto financing dealers talk the talk - but don’t walk the walk - when it comes to meeting the needs of their customers. They stock their lots with “bottom of the barrel” vehicles unlikely to last the length of their loans. DriveTime dealers carefully selects used vehicles and treats every vehicle with a pre-purchase inspection*.  When customers arrive at the lots, there are two paths they can take, either vehicle shopping or financing-based recommendations, the latter is what we recommend.","At DriveTime, we believe obtaining poor credit auto financing in %REGION% shouldn’t mean settling for a less desirable car. Unlike many of our competitors, we scour the market for the best selection of vehicles to stock our lots. When customers come in to shop for their next used car, our attentive sales staff works to identify which vehicle they will most easily afford and enjoy."],["At DriveTime, we believe obtaining %REGION% auto financing should be possible for anyone with a steady income and the ability to pay. Regardless of your past credit problems or lack of credit history, we will work with you to determine which vehicles and financing plans work best fit your budget. Then, we will help you set up financing with a payment schedule to help you establish more credit history.","When shopping for auto financing in %REGION%, you may be used to rejection from other used car lots. Although our competitors constantly look for reasons to say “no” to customers, we are committed to saying “yes.” Two of the most important documents we need from you are proof of steady income and your credit past, allowing us to present to you the most affordable financing plans for your budget.","Call us crazy, but we believe dealers advertising “poor credit auto financing” should actually provide auto financing to people with poor credit! This is why we continually work with poor credit customers to find the best financing option that’s as distinct as our customers. DriveTime dealers review your income and credit history along with a few other necessary documents, connect you with the right financing plan, and do everything possible to help you succeed at making on-time payments.","Does it seem like every %REGION% auto financing dealer has turned you down - even those offering poor credit auto financing? At DriveTime, we commit to financing prospective vehicle shoppers with all types of credit. We understand the many circumstances that lead to damaged credit and we want to see you succeed in the future. That’s why we work to find the ideal payment arrangements to keep you on track and behind the wheel."],["Far more important than your financial past is your present and future. For those seeking auto financing in %REGION%, DriveTime dealers provide the opportunity to get behind the wheel of a used car while also establishing credit history.   Stop by a DriveTime auto financing dealership today to discuss the financing options and vehicles that may be available to you! <br><br> * DriveTime is not able to make safety recall repairs, so vehicles may be subject to open recalls.  Visit http://www.safercar.gov/ for more information about recalls.","If you are looking to build upon your credit history, DriveTime reports its auto financing to all 3 credit bureaus. Not only do our customers achieve their goals of car ownership; they receive the opportunity to show creditors they are capable of making their payments on time every month. Contact us today to learn how %REGION% auto financing from DriveTime can help. <br><br> * DriveTime is not able to make safety recall repairs, so vehicles may be subject to open recalls.  Visit http://www.safercar.gov/ for more information about recalls.","At DriveTime, poor credit auto financing is a means to an end. We help you get into the car you need while simultaneously reporting your payment history on your auto financing. We report all our auto financing customers to all 3 credit bureaus on a regular basis. Customers who have more positive, on-time payment history may increase their credit score, opening door for new financing options. <br><br>* DriveTime is not able to make safety recall repairs, so vehicles may be subject to open recalls.  Visit http://www.safercar.gov/ for more information about recalls.","DriveTime looks at your credit past differently than traditional financing institutions.  As long as you have a steady income and reasonable credit history, we extend the poor credit auto financing %REGION% residents of most credit profiles. Drive off a DriveTime lot today in a new-to-you used car and enjoy the convenience and ease of our several payment options.   Paying on-time provides you more credit history and potentially more financing options down the road. <br><br> * DriveTime is not able to make safety recall repairs, so vehicles may be subject to open recalls.  Visit http://www.safercar.gov/ for more information about recalls."]],"ArticleSection":"Automotive Finance","AuthorFirstName":"Sara","AuthorLastName":"Davis","DatePublished":"2014-12-01T00:00:00"}' 
