ate our determination to set ourselves apart from such establishments.","Although %REGION% “Buy Here Pay Here” car lots treat consumers as though they are the only option available to those with less than ideal credit, few things could be further from the truth. Working with these dealers opens customers up to the risk of shoddy vehicles and unreasonable payment plans. Come to DriveTime to buy your next van, car, SUV, or truck and see the difference.","When seeking a used car in %REGION%, avoid buying into the lie that “Buy Here Pay Here” dealers are your only option. The majority of these businesses will take your hard-earned cash, providing little in return. At DriveTime, we offer a distinguished selection of cars, SUVs, vans, and trucks, as well as a wide array of financing options for vehicles to meet your budget. Our in-house financing company reports all your payments to the credit bureaus."]],"ArticleSection":"Bad Credit Loans","AuthorFirstName":"Sara","AuthorLastName":"Davis","DatePublished":"2014-12-01T00:00:00"}' 
